    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "93F\nTWA\nThe only nonstop\nTO CAIRO\nTWA:",
      "Low Introductory Fares\nFrom $749 to $949 Roundtrip*\nSchedules\nNonstop Flight 882\nDeparts JFK\n7:30 p.m.\nMonday\nThursday\nSaturday\nNonstop Flight 883\nDeparts Cairo\n9:30 a.m.\nMonday\nWednesday\nSaturday\n*$749 apex fare New York/Cairo/New York; $949 apex fare Los\nAngeles/Cairo/Los Angeles. $3 departure tax not included. Restrictions\napply. Call TWA or your travel agent.\nFrom October 31st, you can fly non-stop to the\nexotic allure of Cairo from New York's Kennedy\nInternational Airport. Take advantage of our low\nintroductory fares.\nChoose one of TWA's 12 Getaway Tours of\nEgypt and the Middle East. See the Pyramids\nof Giza, the golden treasures of Tut, the temples\nof Luxor and Karnak, the dazzling valley of\nthe kings.\nNonstop wonders, nonstop on TWA\nTWA",
      "INTRODUCING\nnonstop flights from\nNew York to Cairo on TWA\nTWA"
    ],
